No. 1271,

Misc.

Barlow et al. v. Collins, Executive Director, Alabama Agricultural Stabilization and Conservation Service, et al. Jonathan Weiss, Alvin J. Bronstein, Donald A. Jelinek, Charles S. Conley, and Richard B. Sobol for petitioners. Solicitor General Griswold, Assistant Attorney General Ruckelshaus, Peter L. Strauss, Alan S. Rosenthal, and Norman G. Knopf for respondents.

C. A. 5th Cir. Motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis granted. Cer-tiorari granted and case transferred to appellate docket.
